<figure id="fig-ch42_01_02" class="ost-tag-lo-apbio-ch33-s01-lo01"><media id="fs-idp217830864" alt="Micrograph shows a blood smear. Red blood cells are disk-shaped, and pinched together in the center. Monocytes, lymphocytes and neutrophils are all ball-shaped and fuzzy. Platelets are small, flat disks.">
