<exercise id="fs-id1166172587471">
<problem id="fs-id1166170613820">
<para id="fs-id1166174627555"><emphasis>Describe</emphasis> the difference between the mammalian cell-mediated and humoral responses to a pathogen. Include in your description the roles of antigens and antibodies, T-cells, B-cells, inoculation with vaccines, and the relative response times.</para></problem>
</exercise>
